<!DOCTYPE topic SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<topic title="Card properties page"><warning>Card properties describe how
Mingle manages project workflow. Adding, changing or deleting card properties
has a major impact on the project team. Ensure you understand card properties
before changing values on this page.</warning> <section
title="What you can do on this page"> <p>The Card properties page is where you
can view, add, delete or edit the <cref
topic="card_properties">properties</cref> (variables) that can be attached to
cards, e.g. software feature, status, priority, iteration.</p> <p>From this
page you can edit property names, show or hide properties (so they're
conditionally visible/invisible on cards), mark properties as <cref
topic="transition_only_properties">transition only</cref>, and lock or unlock
properties.</p> 

